    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "siege_weapon",
        "text": "While the official name of this contraption is the \u201cportable catapult,\u201d it gained the name \u201cteekdoon\u201d as a reference to the weapon\u2019s initial inspiration: the diving takedowns of peregrine falcons. However, it replaces elegant dives with the brute force of falling weights that hit targets from above.",
